name: Young, High and Dead - Blu Ray (PAL)
description:
Purchase a 'Pre-release' copy of the film on Blu Ray. These are early limited release copies ahead of the main production line that will roll out summer of 2014.

FREE Postage for all UK based customers.

Please note copies are PAL so please ensure your Blu Ray player meets this spec and/or is region free. If you would like an NTSC copy please contact rumpunchproductions@gmail.com
